## Definition

A _$(2,1)$-site_ is an [[(âˆž,1)-site]]. whose underlying [[(âˆž,1)-category]] is a [[(2,1)-category]].

An [[(âˆž,1)-sheaf]] on a $(2,1)$-site is a [[(2,1)-sheaf]]/[[stack]].

